<h2>Claim Status Update - {{claimNumber}}</h2>

<p>Hello {{claimantName}},</p>

<p>Your claim status has been updated. Here are the details:</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3>Claim Information</h3>
    <table class="info-table">
        <tr>
            <td>Claim Number:</td>
            <td><strong>{{claimNumber}}</strong></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Policy Number:</td>
            <td>{{policyNumber}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>New Status:</td>
            <td><span class="badge badge-{{statusColor}}">{{status}}</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Updated By:</td>
            <td>{{updatedBy}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Update Date:</td>
            <td>{{formatDateTime updatedAt}}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

{{#if notes}}
<div class="alert alert-info">
    <h4>Update Notes</h4>
    <p>{{notes}}</p>
</div>
{{/if}}

{{#ifEquals status "approved"}}
<div class="alert alert-success">
    <h4>‚úÖ Claim Approved</h4>
    <p>Your claim has been approved and is being processed. You will receive further communication regarding payment or service arrangements.</p>
</div>
{{else ifEquals status "rejected"}}
<div class="alert alert-danger">
    <h4>‚ùå Claim Rejected</h4>
    <p>Your claim has been rejected. Please contact our claims department for more information about the rejection reason.</p>
</div>
{{else ifEquals status "in_review"}}
<div class="alert alert-warning">
    <h4>üîç Claim Under Review</h4>
    <p>Your claim is currently under review by our claims team. We will contact you if additional information is required.</p>
</div>
{{else}}
<div class="alert alert-info">
    <h4>Status Update</h4>
    <p>Your claim status has been updated to: <strong>{{status}}</strong></p>
</div>
{{/ifEquals}}

<p>If you have any questions about this status update, please contact our claims department.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
<strong>SDK Admin Portal Claims Team</strong></p> 